Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.06,1:06:30.40,2,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的这场戏 实际上是一整幕的戏\NToday's scene,which is the entire act in fact
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.49,1:06:35.47,2,NTP,0,0,0,,非常壮烈的场面 因为我们将失去两位角色\NIs so huge because we are losing two of our characters
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.51,1:06:42.22,2,NTP,0,0,0,,马上要开拍了 Gomez已经在枪战过后躺在地上牺牲了 \NThe scene is gonna open and Gomez is already dead on the ground after the shoot-out
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.41,1:06:49.81,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Hank已经受重伤但并不致命 但他今天还是会死\NAnd hank is severely wounded but not mortally,and he is gonna die today
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.91,1:07:01.07,2,NTP,0,0,0,,卡 漂亮 看看呐\NCut it,beautiful,check that,check it in
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.16,1:07:05.99,2,NTP,0,0,0,,其实有点怪  你知道 就要死了就要死了\NIt was kind of weird that,you know the idea,it's coming and it's coming
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.06,1:07:08.29,2,NTP,0,0,0,,然后死期到了 过程很难熬\NAnd then there you are,it was trying time
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.38,1:07:10.04,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是 在那拍摄很辛苦\NI mean,it was tough shooting out there
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.11,1:07:13.26,2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在你很努力表演的时候 沙子不断飘进你眼睛里\NIf you are trying to do a scene and the sand is getting in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.32,1:07:18.90,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是拍摄的好地方 这样的态度也不行\NIt was not great circumstances to shoot,so that kind of attitude too
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.78,1:07:31.80,2,NTP,0,0,0,,很长一段时间以来 Dean的角色是黑白分明的\NFor a long time,Dean's character things were black and white
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.87,1:07:33.81,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他成了道德中心\NAnd he became sort of the moral center
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.87,1:07:38.27,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他在办的这整个Heisenberg案子\NThis whole Heisenberg chase that he has been on
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.36,1:07:40.29,2,NTP,0,0,0,,真的测试出了他的本性\NHas really tested what he's made of
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.59,1:07:45.57,2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是Hank最终选择了正义的一方\NBut hank ultimately chooses what is right
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.56,1:07:52.13,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是助理特工主管Schrader  你他妈的去死吧\NMy name is ASAC schrader and you can fuck yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.21,1:07:57.03,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Hank 你得配合我 好吗\NHank,you got to work with me here OK
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.11,1:08:02.73,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Hank一开始就知道完了\NHank knows from the beginning that it's over
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.79,1:08:06.49,2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是Walt还在哀求他们放过Hank \NAnd Walt is still trying to beg them to not shoot hank,to kill him
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.57,1:08:08.61,2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是Hank知道这于事无补\NBut hank knew it wouldn't matter,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.70,1:08:13.71,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我见过最聪明的人\NYou are the smartest man I've ever met
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.78,1:08:20.68,2,NTP,0,0,0,,但你却不知道他十分钟之前就做好决定了\NBut you can't see that he made up his mind 10 minutes ago
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.79,1:08:24.31,2,NTP,0,0,0,,当你直视Dean的眼睛的时候 你能看到他给Hank带来的特质\NYou look into Dean's eyes and you are seeing what he's bringing to it
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.42,1:08:26.82,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你能看见他内在的力量\NYou can see this inner strength there
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.90,1:08:31.52,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这几乎是整部剧里Hank这个角色的核心\NThat's kind of has been the heart of hank throughout the whole series
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.62,1:08:33.86,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以看到他最后一刻的镇定从容\NAnd seeing that poise through the final moments
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.97,1:08:37.16,2,NTP,0,0,0,,对 这就是最适合他的 壮烈的谢幕方式\NYeah,that's the way you go out
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.20,1:08:50.32,2,NTP,0,0,0,,拍得很漂亮 恰到好处 尽管情节很悲伤 但能感到正义\NIt's beautiful,and it feels right,and as sad as it is,if feels just
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.43,1:08:53.25,2,NTP,0,0,0,,与《X档案》的某些正义元素类似\NAnd it feels like the right kind of X-File character
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.62,1:09:02.05,2,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见 兄弟\NSee you tomorrow,bro
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.48,1:09:09.97,2,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地终于走了 麻烦蛋一个\NThank god he's gone some pain in the ass he is,oh my god
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.80,1:09:14.27,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会在他面前说他坏话的\NI would never,you know,say it in front of him
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.35,1:09:16.62,2,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我挺乐意拍下来\NAnd I certainly want this recorded
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.89,1:09:23.42,2,NTP,0,0,0,,神呐 生活突然变美好了\NGod,our lives all just got a little better right now
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.14,1:09:26.40,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你说呢\NWhat do you think
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.64,1:09:36.08,2,NTP,0,0,0,,坦诚点 真的 开口吧\NJust be yourself,that's all,just ask,man
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.17,1:09:38.94,2,NTP,0,0,0,,-你知我知 -有人摄像\NIt's a safe conversation -what about the camera..
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.06,1:09:42.13,2,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哦 这什么时候冒出来的    \NWow,when do that appear
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.75,1:09:54.14,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Hank被杀的情节 实际拍了两天\NKilling hank actually happened two days
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.23,1:09:55.56,2,NTP,0,0,0,,第一天他被杀\NHe was shot on one day
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.65,1:09:57.97,2,NTP,0,0,0,,而在第二天他的尸体被人拖走 扔到一个洞里\NAnd then the next his body was dragged and dropped in the hole
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.05,1:10:00.50,2,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这家伙 让我马上就能头部中弹了\NHe's the guy,bullet in the fucking head right now
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.92,1:10:03.68,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那个妆看起来像个粉刺\Nlooks like a pimple right now
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.61,1:10:08.14,2,NTP,0,0,0,,助理特工主管Hank Schrader 外号小粉刺\NThe pimple the A Hank Schrader
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.72,1:10:17.81,2,NTP,0,0,0,,锁定二台记得看我 混蛋们\NCatch me on channel 2 motherfuckers
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.91,1:10:21.22,2,NTP,0,0,0,,好的好的 开始拍了\NOK,here we go here we go,walk away
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.81,1:10:24.57,2,NTP,0,0,0,,喊开拍后 你们拖着他走\NYou guys are dragging him on action
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.94,1:10:32.60,2,NTP,0,0,0,,开拍\NAction
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.97,1:10:42.84,2,NTP,0,0,0,,停\NCut it
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.91,1:10:47.40,2,NTP,0,0,0,,继续拖啊 伙计们\NKeep dragging him guys,keep going
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.72,1:10:54.22,2,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 万众瞩目的一刻来了\NAlright guys,it's the moment everyone's been waiting for
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.31,1:10:58.10,2,NTP,0,0,0,,整整60集之后\N60 episodes later
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.19,1:11:01.13,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Dean Norris谢幕\NDean Norris
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.81,1:11:07.66,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFF00&\pos(314,36)}去CBS拍《穹顶之下》
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.81,1:11:07.66,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去CBS了\NYou are going on to CBS
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.74,1:11:11.53,2,NTP,0,0,0,,百万观众都能看你笑话了\NWhere millions and millions more people will see through your inadequacy
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.72,1:11:19.61,2,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你们一切顺利\NWe wish you all the best to and everybody else
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.42,1:11:23.78,2,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 我们会想你的\NThank you man.that's.. -we're gonna miss you
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.87,1:11:25.89,2,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了 伙计 -很开心\NAppreciate it thank you guys -it's been a pleasure...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.16,1:11:29.71,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这是嘛玩意啊\NWhat the fuck is this
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.36,1:11:32.56,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你也有\NAnd you too
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.71,1:11:40.60,2,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们 谢谢\NThank you guys,thanks a lot
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.13,1:11:45.79,2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你在我们拍首播集的时候告诉我\NIf you told me back in the first day of shooting,the pilot episode
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.90,1:11:48.33,2,NTP,0,0,0,,大结局的时候我会多难过\NHow sad I was gonna be at the end of all
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.40,1:11:50.71,2,NTP,0,0,0,,眼看Hank这个角色离开\NTo see the character Hank Schrader go
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.79,1:11:53.58,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我会很惊讶\NI think it would have surprised me because
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.66,1:11:56.81,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没将Hank预想成一个多么有趣的角色\NI didn't foresee the character being all that interesting
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.88,1:11:59.44,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他就是那种 热情友好的男子汉\NI thought of him as kind of an hail-fellow-well-met
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.54,1:12:04.26,2,NTP,0,0,0,,耀武扬威的家伙 和Walt完全不一样\NMacho swaggering guy who is everything that Walter White was not
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.27,1:12:09.60,2,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们选中了Dean来演这个角色 而Dean要比那丰富得多\NThen we cast Dean Norris,and Dean is so much more than that
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.67,1:12:15.40,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个复杂的人 很出色 很多面的人\NHe is a complicated man and a wonderful man who has a lot of layers
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.77,1:12:20.98,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法想象这部剧没了Dean会变成什么样\NAnd I can't imagine what the show would have been without Dean Norris playing hank
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.08,1:12:24.85,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你能感觉到就快大结局了\NYou feel closures happening
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.94,1:12:29.00,2,NTP,0,0,0,,每次我们拍完一集 就感觉会有扇门被关上\NLittle doors,each time we get to another stop little doors are closing
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.06,1:12:33.34,2,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐 哥们儿\NOh my god,yeah.brother
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.72,1:12:42.09,2,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越难过 越来越悲伤了 \NIt's getting nastier and sadder,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.28,1:12:44.73,2,NTP,0,0,0,,非常正确 Anna你准备好了吗\NThat's correct,anna are you ready
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.80,1:12:49.70,2,NTP,0,0,0,,预备 3 2 1 开拍\NHere we go,rolling and 3,2,1,action
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.80,1:13:08.10,2,NTP,0,0,0,,不 求你了... Walt\NNo,please.....Walt
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.21,1:13:10.98,2,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮\NBeautifully done
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.49,1:13:19.03,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那场戏是六年来我这个角色的高潮\NThat scene was the culmination for me of 6 years of the show
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.11,1:13:23.62,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这场戏会有多难拍 多有挑战性\NI knew how difficult that was gonna be,how challenging it was gonna be
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.20,1:13:29.14,2,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们特地为我准备了个小房间 \NSo they had a little bedroom for me and
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.21,1:13:32.83,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我走进去一直待在那里\NI went in there and I just kept myself in that zone
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.99,1:13:36.96,2,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他们走进来说 对不起 我们得等一段时间 下雪了\NAnd then they came in and said sorry,we gotta hold,it's snowing
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.34,1:13:43.39,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不得不在那里坐了一整天\NI had to kind of sit on it the whole day
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.53,1:13:48.56,2,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他们再进来跟我说 雪停了 可以继续了\NThen they came back and said OK,it stopped snowing,we were ready to go now
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.58,1:14:13.13,2,NTP,0,0,0,,求你停下来  求你了 求你了\NPlease stop,please,please...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.93,1:14:31.05,2,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候对于一个演员 会有这种情况\NSometimes what happens is an actor,is you get to the moment
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.17,1:14:36.16,2,NTP,0,0,0,,当需要你投身进去的时候 你的身体说不行\NWhen it's time to give it over,and your body says I don't want to
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.89,1:14:40.32,2,NTP,0,0,0,,因为陷进去很可怕\NBecause it's scary
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.44,1:14:44.69,2,NTP,0,0,0,,在我前几条NG后 Rian到我身边来\NRian came up to me after the first few passes
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.78,1:14:47.45,2,NTP,0,0,0,,对我说 听着 你不必担心跌倒在街上\NAnd said to me listen,you don't have to worry about falling down to the street
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.55,1:14:49.72,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我说我只是害怕\NAnd I said I am just scared
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.30,1:14:56.44,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他就说 我能理解 没事的\NAnd he said,yeah,OK,OK
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.71,1:15:01.99,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道 我需要有人真心地牵着我的手\NHe just knew that I needed somebody to essentially take my hand
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.07,1:15:05.38,2,NTP,0,0,0,,真诚地说 你很安全\NIn essence to say,you are safe
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.33,1:15:10.50,2,NTP,0,0,0,,准备拍了\NRoll it
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.59,1:15:12.93,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他看着我 \NAnd he looked at me and he saw it
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.01,1:15:15.67,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他说 行了 他就默默地转过身 说 开拍吧\NAnd he said OK,and he turned around quietly and said let's go
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.75,1:15:19.58,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他走开了 我们继续拍 然后我们做到了\NAnd he walked away,and there we were,and then we did it
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.67,1:15:29.70,2,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 \NPlease,please....
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.81,1:15:37.34,2,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很真实\NIt feels so real
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.42,1:15:44.84,2,NTP,0,0,0,,因为Anna把自己当成了Skyler 经历着情感上的跌宕起伏\NBecause anna put herself in Skyler's shoes on that emotional roller-coaster
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.34,1:15:51.07,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我想对得起那么漂亮的剧本\NI want to honor that beautiful piece of writing
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.16,1:15:52.85,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把这个角色塑造得很好\NAnd I want to honor that character
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.98,1:15:56.11,2,NTP,0,0,0,,尽我所能地演好\NBy giving it everything I know I have to give it
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.18,1:16:01.03,2,NTP,0,0,0,,后来我谢谢他帮了我\NAfterwards when I thanked him for helping me
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.12,1:16:04.90,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他说 我和这可没关系 是你的功劳\NHe said,well,I didn't have anything to do,I mean,you did it all
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.97,1:16:07.52,2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 是他帮助我做到的\NBut you know,he helped make it happen
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.91,1:16:17.70,2,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候我起床投几个篮\NSometimes I get up and just kind of shoot a basket
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.78,1:16:19.75,2,NTP,0,0,0,,得到灵感 然后再休息\NAnd get inspiration and take a break
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.43,1:16:23.84,2,NTP,0,0,0,,《绝命毒师》其实有两个中心\NFor Breaking Bad there's really two centers of the show
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.92,1:16:26.01,2,NTP,0,0,0,,一个是Albuquerque的制作中心\NThere's the production center in Albuquerque
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.10,1:16:27.93,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我们的演员和工作人员主要待的地方\NWhere our cast and crews spend most of their time
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.01,1:16:32.55,2,NTP,0,0,0,,然后还有我们的后期与编剧中心 在加州的Burbank\NAnd then there's our post-production and our writing center here Burbank California
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.53,1:16:36.81,2,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 反基督徒先生 我不会让你把这件事搞砸的\Nlook,Mr. Natural,I'm not gonna let you sabotage this thing
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.89,1:16:40.06,2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你磕飞了去找他 他是不会带你走的\NThis guy is not gonna take you if you show up high
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.13,1:16:42.45,2,NTP,0,0,0,,别闹了 这关乎我俩的性命\NSo stop screwing around,or it's both our asses
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.40,1:16:45.74,2,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上 你制作一部电视剧要走三遍\NBasically you make an episode of TV 3 times
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.82,1:16:48.50,2,NTP,0,0,0,,首先你写好剧本 然后拍摄 最后剪辑\NFirst you write it,you shoot it,and you edit it
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.59,1:16:50.43,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要把故事说三遍\NYou got to tell the story 3 times
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.88,1:16:55.39,2,NTP,0,0,0,,所以33%的《绝命毒师》\NA big 33% of the story telling in Breaking Bad happened
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.48,1:16:58.98,2,NTP,0,0,0,,是在McDonald和Dixon的剪辑室里完成的 \NIn those editing rooms of McDonald and Dixon
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.06,1:17:01.48,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这些我都喜欢 我们超时多少了\NI love all those stuff,how much over are we
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.23,1:17:04.79,2,NTP,0,0,0,,144秒 我坚持保留这段的唯一原因是\N144s,the only reason I'm insisting this
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.86,1:17:06.23,2,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是唯一一次的\NIs because this is the only time
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.31,1:17:11.92,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他把大麻放进了口袋里的场景\NThat he's got this weed,and he's putting it in his pocket
