Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.44,1:25:51.73,2,NTP,0,0,0,,兰伯特先生 欢迎来到新罕布什尔州\NMr.Lambert,welcome to New Hampshire
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.02,1:25:56.20,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正处在森蒂亚峰顶\NWe are at top of the Sandia Crest
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.28,1:25:59.14,2,NTP,0,0,0,,第一批西班牙探险者给它命的名\NThe original Spanish explorers named that
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.22,1:26:05.28,2,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一到晚上 这座山就会沐浴在橙红的夕阳之中\NCuz' in the evening this mountain are lit up in beautiful red orange
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.39,1:26:08.77,2,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来像一片西瓜 Sandia在西语中就是西瓜的意思 所以这样叫\NThey look like a big slice of watermelon,that's why it's called sandía
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.85,1:26:10.28,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正处在山顶\NWe're at top of them right now
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.44,1:26:13.27,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这座山俯瞰Albuquerque城\NAnd they overlook Albuquerque
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.36,1:26:15.04,2,NTP,0,0,0,,所以直线距离上 我们其实没走那么远\NSo we are not that far as a crow-fly
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.12,1:26:17.13,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这离我们的摄影棚也不远\NThat far away from our sound stages
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.20,1:26:22.42,2,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说 这就好像是在拍David Lean或者Stanley Kubrick的片子一样\NTo me,this is like me getting to play David Lean or Stanley Kubrick
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.50,1:26:23.65,2,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们建造了这样的布景\NBecause of something we've got to build
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.73,1:26:26.19,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要在现场拍摄小屋的外景\NExterior of this cabin on location
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.28,1:26:28.25,2,NTP,0,0,0,,而内景则在舞台拍摄\NAnd we have the interior on stage
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.34,1:26:30.13,2,NTP,0,0,0,,小屋不仅仅像《闪灵》中的山顶酒店\NNot only like the Overlook Hotel
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.21,1:26:32.48,2,NTP,0,0,0,,光是看上去就很棒\NI think it's looking just fantastic
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.57,1:26:36.76,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本没法在你们觉得正好的时机把门关上\NBut I will never be able to close the door,that would be,at timing you enjoy
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.86,1:26:40.37,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来看看是什么问题 -好\NLet's see what happens -alright
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.36,1:26:46.34,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢硬汉角色 传统的老式的纯正硬汉角色\NI love tough guys,good old-fashioned old-school tough guys
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.43,1:26:50.49,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不是那种炫耀卖弄的人 而是安静的人\NNot guys who poster and flex,but guys who are quiet
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.59,1:26:52.93,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Mike就是这种硬汉\NMike Ehmantraut is one of the tough guys
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.41,1:26:57.06,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Robert Forster同样也是这种硬汉的代表\NAnd Robert Forster represents another one of those tough guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.16,1:26:58.82,2,NTP,0,0,0,,一个月以后见\NSee you in a month
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.94,1:27:04.54,2,NTP,0,0,0,,每一次接到新对白 演员们都是从零开始的\NThe actor starts at zero with every new piece of dialogue.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.63,1:27:07.32,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他需要在短短的拍摄时间内 从零分达到十分\NHe is trying to get to ten by the time he finishing shooting
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.44,1:27:10.63,2,NTP,0,0,0,,而且每次都必须走一遍从零到十的过程\NYou got to go from 0 to 10 for every single time
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.71,1:27:13.01,2,NTP,0,0,0,,先前的工作经验并不会带来什么优势\NThere's no advantage to having worked before
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.09,1:27:18.13,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你得以新材料为起点 认真学习它\NYou got to start it with new material and learn it and fan it out
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.24,1:27:20.15,2,NTP,0,0,0,,把它理解透彻 并且全力投入地表演\NAnd understand it and try to mean it
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.57,1:27:23.38,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你为这花了大钱\NYou paid good money for this
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.45,1:27:26.48,2,NTP,0,0,0,,在这你有两英亩的地盘 很多树 还有个暖和的地方住\NYou got two acres up here. Lots of woods,a nice warm place
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.40,1:27:31.72,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这儿正是一个能让人休息思索的好地方\NSeems to me just the spot for a man to rest up,think on things
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.61,1:27:37.63,2,NTP,0,0,0,,四处看看的话 风景不错\NIf you look around,it's beautiful
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.46,1:27:40.31,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮了大忙 谢谢你\NYou've been very helpful. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.11,1:27:42.95,2,NTP,0,0,0,,一个月以后见\NSee you in a month
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.04,1:27:49.49,2,NTP,0,0,0,,编剧室走过六个年头了 -对啊\NIt's been 6 years in this room -yeah it has been
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.36,1:27:54.02,2,NTP,0,0,0,,2007年就开始了 -真难以相信啊\N2007 -hard to believe,can't
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.10,1:27:56.61,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那会儿还是艾森豪威尔当政吧\NEisenhower was president
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.69,1:28:00.15,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们最后的剧情卡片了 第五季第十六集的\NThese are our last couple of cards of E516
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.23,1:28:03.82,2,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是全剧第六十二集《绝命毒师》的最后一集\NWhich is the episode 62,which is the very last episode ever for the Breaking Bad
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.90,1:28:07.13,2,NTP,0,0,0,,能把这些卡片贴上去么 -好的\NYou wanna start putting some of those up -yep
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.82,1:28:14.17,2,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一次拜访....他挚爱的实验室..\N.....meth lab,last visit,to his precious.....
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.51,1:28:23.48,2,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 要贴最后一张了 要贴最后一张了\NOK,last card,last card,alright
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.66,1:28:25.18,2,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊 不要啊\NDon't do it don't do it
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.26,1:28:27.69,2,NTP,0,0,0,,每一季完结后 我们都会庆祝\NWe celebrate every time we end a season on Breaking Bad
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.77,1:28:29.41,2,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是喜欢用香槟来庆祝\NWe typically celebrate with champagne
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.53,1:28:31.28,2,NTP,0,0,0,,在编剧室挂上最后一张卡片\NIn the writers room we put up the last card
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.36,1:28:33.42,2,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉像是非常隆重的一刻\NAnd it feels like a very momentous occasion
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.49,1:28:37.37,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有个小小的传统 我们会把标有集数的卡片挂起来\NWe have a little tradition we put up the number of the episode
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.45,1:28:41.02,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这张正好是第五季第十六集的 马上就挂它了\NThis one happens to be 516 and we put it up
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.11,1:28:48.08,2,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一件事 就是把它挂在这个角落 嗯... 好了\NSo last thing we do,we put it up on the corner here...and...bingo
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.27,1:29:05.30,2,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了《绝命毒师》编剧室的工作到此结束\NThis is the end,this is the end of the Breaking Bad writer's room right here
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.64,1:29:11.56,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这一次的结束 比以往任何一次都伤感\NThis time was sadder than other times in the past
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.65,1:29:13.68,2,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们知道这会是最后一次了\NBecause we knew for sure it's the last time
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.65,1:29:16.33,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为我感到的是悲伤\NYou know I think I feel sad about it
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.42,1:29:18.58,2,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上我感到的却是有点麻木了 真是吓一跳\NInstead I just feel kind of numb,I was a bit in shock
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.49,1:29:24.34,2,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 到现在几个月的时间了 我还没去消化这件事\NAnd I still haven't processed it many months later now
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.42,1:29:25.91,2,NTP,0,0,0,,给最后几集做剪辑的时候 \NAs we edited the final episodes
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.00,1:29:29.19,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没意识到它已经完结了\NIt still hasn't a completely dawned on me that it's over
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.26,1:29:33.41,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是标志结束的重大时刻 最后一张卡片被挂上去的时候 \NThat was a big moment of ending that last card going up
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.50,1:29:36.03,2,NTP,0,0,0,,工作里面最难的部分 就是往后写剧情\NThat's the hardest part of the job breaking the episodes
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.12,1:29:37.16,2,NTP,0,0,0,,当最后一片剧情卡被挂上去的时候 \NWhen that last one goes up
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.25,1:29:40.06,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你就真正认识到 自己终于要停产了\NYou really know you finally are out of childbirth
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.14,1:29:44.00,2,NTP,0,0,0,,敬我们最棒的编剧 最棒的演员\NA toast to the best writers,best actors
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.08,1:29:48.62,2,NTP,0,0,0,,最棒的制片 以及最棒的所有的工作人员 你们永远是最棒的\NBest producers,best crew on TV ever now and forever
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.70,1:29:52.09,2,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢所有人 你们的努力成就了这部剧\NThank you for all you guys for making the show what it's been.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.01,1:29:55.31,2,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝保佑你们 -干杯\NGod bless you. -cheers.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.14,1:30:08.65,2,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是2013年3月10号 我和Aaron在我的Albuquerque居所\NIt's march 10th,2013 We are at my house in Albuquerque
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.75,1:30:13.73,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正准备读《绝命毒师》最后一集的剧本\NHe's Aaron,I'm Bryan we are reading the last episode of Breaking Bad
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.84,1:30:17.35,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还没看过..是的 我们不知道会怎样\NWe haven't read it yet....we don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.42,1:30:18.86,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正喝啤酒呢\NAnd we are having beer
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.72,1:30:23.63,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是超级郁闷 该来的终于要来了\NI am so unbelievably depressed that this is happening right now
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.71,1:30:26.06,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你们都懂的\NI know you all understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.14,1:30:31.73,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这对我来说真的是很私人化的经历 大约每隔一周拿到剧本\NIt was such a personal experience to get the scripts every other week,about
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.84,1:30:34.91,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你私下读着它们\NAnd you privately read them and
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.99,1:30:39.33,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你会受到剧情的冲击并产生个人情感\NHave your own personal sensation of..an impact of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.42,1:30:42.45,2,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这是最后一季了\NAnd since this was going to the very last season
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.57,1:30:48.20,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我想 我们也许可以在镜头前 朗读这段最后的剧本\NI thought what if we read the very last script cold on camera
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.30,1:30:51.14,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是结束了\NThis is it..
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.23,1:30:57.71,2,NTP,0,0,0,,开车去他家 泊车 进了门 喝杯啤酒\NJust going in there,picking up a beer,driving there and parking...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.78,1:31:01.14,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕临近结束的每分每秒\NI was dreading every moment of it
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.24,1:31:08.95,2,NTP,0,0,0,,砰砰砰...整间屋子爆发着机枪的怒吼\NBah bah bah...the entire room erupts in machine gunfire
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.04,1:31:13.59,2,NTP,0,0,0,,闪着红光的枪弹穿透墙壁\NRed tazers ripped through the walls
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.69,1:31:16.42,2,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是《星际迷航》里的相位枪发出来的\NLike Phaser beams right out of star trek
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.52,1:31:18.44,2,NTP,0,0,0,,弹雨撂倒了Jack及其同伙\NCutting through jack's gang
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.58,1:31:20.63,2,NTP,0,0,0,,好似滚烫的刀锋划入一块黄油那般利索\NLike hot knifes through butter
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.57,1:31:25.31,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那架巨大的M-60机枪先前被摆在小道上\NThat big M-60 has been placed in their sideways
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.39,1:31:27.88,2,NTP,0,0,0,,安置在那个Walt组装的装置的顶上\NMounted at the the top of the rig Walt built
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.97,1:31:30.46,2,NTP,0,0,0,,它咯吱发响 前后来回扫动\NIt rattles away,sweeping back and forth
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.54,1:31:32.92,2,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是撒旦的雨刷器一样\NLike Satan's windshield wiper
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.67,1:31:37.98,2,NTP,0,0,0,,大家准备好吧 这个注定要发生的\NPrepare yourselves people,cuz' it is happening
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.62,1:31:44.56,2,NTP,0,0,0,,说出来 说这是你想要的\NSay the words,say you want this
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.58,1:31:48.93,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你不开口 那什么都不会发生\NNothing happens until I hear you say it
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.18,1:31:51.63,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我想要的\NI want this.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.69,1:31:58.71,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Jesse思考片刻 哗啦一声把枪丢在了地上\NJesse figured as much,he let the gun clatter to the floor
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.46,1:32:01.89,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就自己动手吧\NThen do it yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.98,1:32:05.15,2,NTP,0,0,0,,说完这句 他便转身离开了\NWith that,he turns and walks out
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.09,1:32:09.76,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他和Jesse最后相视良久\NHe and Jesse share one last long look
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.84,1:32:12.82,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Jesse挂上档 开动了车\NThen Jesse chunks the car into gear and hunches it
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.00,1:32:15.80,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这辆雪佛兰埃尔卡米诺嗥叫着 冲向夜色\NThe El Camino go squealing away into the night
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.91,1:32:18.15,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Walt站在那里看他离开\NWalt stands there watching him go
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.25,1:32:21.71,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Jesse加足马力冲向铁链紧缩的大门\NJesse speeds up towards the chain-link locked gate
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.82,1:32:24.72,2,NTP,0,0,0,,梆...他冲出大门 好像那根本不算什么\NBang,he smashes through it like it was nothing
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.81,1:32:27.86,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的镜头离开围场 给Jesse一个特写\NWe leave the compound behind,close angle on Jesse
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.96,1:32:32.35,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他的表情坚毅而无畏 加速奔向黑暗中去\NGrimly-determined,fearing nothing,he speeds towards the darkness
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.44,1:32:34.76,2,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就由我们去想 他将去向何处\NIt's up to us to say where he's headed
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.85,1:32:38.69,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他会有更好的归宿 我能说的就这么多\NI'd like to call it something better,I leave it at that
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.85,1:32:42.49,2,NTP,0,0,0,,俯视 我们从空中往下看到了Walt\NBird's eye view: We look straight down on Walt
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.60,1:32:46.25,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他这时跌倒到地板上 然后平躺着\NAs he tumbles into frame,lying flat on his back on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.35,1:32:49.14,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他的眼睛望向我们 毫无生机\NHis eyes staring up at us,lifeless.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.25,1:32:54.51,2,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 他最后的表情却又流露出那么一丝心满意足\NAnd yet,his final expression is one of faint satisfaction
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.61,1:32:58.58,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们依旧保持俯瞰视角 向下看着他\NWe continue skyward,looking down on Walt
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.70,1:33:01.14,2,NTP,0,0,0,,镜头保持上升 再上升\NRising as high as we can go
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.26,1:33:04.84,2,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢地 从这个画面渐变到一片漆黑\NOff this image,slowly fading to black...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.94,1:33:07.00,2,NTP,0,0,0,,全剧终\NEnd of series
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.80,1:33:13.20,2,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哦 \NWow..
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.56,1:33:21.38,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得不会有续集了\NSo I guess there won't be a sequel
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.80,1:33:24.77,2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是Jesse活下来了 \NBut Jesse stays alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.36,1:33:29.27,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你感觉怎样\NHow do you feel
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.01,1:33:42.14,2,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我有点伤感 很棒 真的 你懂的\NOh man,I feel sad..it's great I mean it's..you know
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.84,1:33:46.67,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这个结局太完美了\NIt's uh..it's perfect
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.12,1:33:53.69,2,NTP,0,0,0,,就绪 -就绪\NSet -set
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.80,1:33:54.78,2,NTP,0,0,0,,开拍\NAnd action
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.00,1:34:04.00,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让我这么做的\NYou want this
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.90,1:34:10.13,2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不想 就不会给我创造这样的条件\NYou wouldn't have brought me all this way if you didn't
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.72,1:34:19.18,2,NTP,0,0,0,,还有谁会比Vince更合适导演最后一集呢 \NWho else would be the person to direct this last episode
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.26,1:34:23.48,2,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁是比Vince Gilligan更合适的人选来将剧情推向结局呢\NWho else should bring this story to a conclusion other than Vince Gilligan
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.59,1:34:25.46,2,NTP,0,0,0,,更窃窃私语一些 更急促一些\NEven more whisper,even quicker
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.52,1:34:31.24,2,NTP,0,0,0,,把我送回家就好 剩下的我能做\NJust get me home.I'll do the rest
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.00,1:34:37.98,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他是整个剧的大脑 他是灵魂和核心所在\NHe is the mastermind,you know he's the soul of it,the heart of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.10,1:34:39.69,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是 你只能看见一个人影\NI mean,all you see is a shape
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.77,1:34:42.11,2,NTP,0,0,0,,但你可以看到这个人正往汽车后座走去\NBut you could see a guy going into the back seat
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.17,1:34:52.38,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Vince应当得到最大的褒奖\NVince Gilligan deserves the lion's share of the preys
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.47,1:34:59.40,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我是部剧的门面 但他和编剧们才是主心骨\NI am the face of it,but he and his writing staff are the backbone
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.42,1:35:05.60,2,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们来说 我认为这就是最好的告别方式\NFor us I think that's how we were able to say goodbye
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.68,1:35:06.85,2,NTP,0,0,0,,就是知道\NIs knowing that
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.94,1:35:13.06,2,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一集中的每个选择都是由Vince定夺的\NEvery choice that was made ultimately came down to him,you know for that last episode
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.15,1:35:18.58,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这让我们所有人都充满了十足的信心和激情\NAnd I think that filled all of us with a lot of confidence and a lot of excitement
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.66,1:35:20.75,2,NTP,0,0,0,,以及对于我们在做的工作 充满了自豪\NAnd a lot of pride in what we are doing
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.84,1:35:27.78,2,NTP,0,0,0,,她没那么可怜...她没那么可怜 -对\NShe's just not sorry enough…She's not sorry enough -right
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.85,1:35:33.76,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是那个失去了一切的人 不是她 -对\NAnd you are the one who's lost everything,not her -right
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.87,1:35:37.34,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你才不在乎她住在一个又小又破的公寓呢 你失去了你的丈夫\NYou don't care she's living in a shabby little apartment,you lost your husband
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.43,1:35:41.17,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这不仅仅是全剧的落幕\NNot only was this the last episode of the series
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.28,1:35:43.19,2,NTP,0,0,0,,但也正是因为 这是全剧的最后一集了\NBut because it was the last episode of the series
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.28,1:35:46.02,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也将迎来许多角色的最后一次表演\NWe were seeing a lot of characters for the last time
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.80,1:35:50.70,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为 演员生涯中会有些难以预料的事情\NI think the life of an actor is very unexpected
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.79,1:35:56.89,2,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会知道你的最后一场戏是你一个人独自演出 \NAnd in their last scene who knows you could find yourself alone in a scene by yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.97,1:36:00.53,2,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个助理导演在你对面帮你读台词配戏\NHaving the assistant director read lines opposite you
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.63,1:36:04.75,2,NTP,0,0,0,,而Betsy就是以这样一种方式谢幕的\NAnd for Betsy's departure that was the case
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.86,1:36:06.35,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 我现在不能接电话\NHello,I can't come to the phone right now
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.43,1:36:08.28,2,NTP,0,0,0,,请在哔的一声后留言\NPlease leave a brief message after the sound of the beep
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.08,1:36:15.40,2,NTP,0,0,0,,是我 我想要真相 行吗\NIt's me…Truth,all right
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.49,1:36:20.10,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这场戏感情上相当复杂 \NThat was a very complicated emotional scene
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.22,1:36:21.66,2,NTP,0,0,0,,但她还要一个人独自完成\NThat she's doing on her own
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.76,1:36:23.57,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解你 Betsy 真的\NI understand,Betsy,I understand
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.68,1:36:25.60,2,NTP,0,0,0,,-这太伤感了... \N-it's sorry to see.... -
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.69,1:36:27.98,2,NTP,0,0,0,,-是的是的 -看到这对姐妹.....\NIt is,it is -these two sisters...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.07,1:36:31.94,2,NTP,0,0,0,,她会为他们俩做任何事 两个人都是\NCuz' she would've done everything for either of them
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.03,1:36:34.99,2,NTP,0,0,0,,拍摄这段时我的心都碎了\NIt broke my heart to shoot that
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.07,1:36:36.64,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟Vince说\NI told Vince that I said that…
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.71,1:36:41.76,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Hank和Marie会为Walt和Skyler做任何事情\NYou know,hank and Marie would have done anything for Walt and Skyler
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.86,1:36:45.71,2,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我也坚信这一点\NAnd I believe that they would have done anything for them
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.81,1:36:49.97,2,NTP,0,0,0,,然而Walt和Skyler却做了那些事情\NAnd then for Walt and Skyler to do what they did
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.07,1:36:54.54,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 只有一种可能Marie会原谅他们\NAnd I said the only way I think Marie could forgive
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.65,1:36:56.12,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是Hank起死回生 \NIs if hank came back
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.23,1:36:57.52,2,NTP,0,0,0,,而那却是不可能的\NAnd that's not happening
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.62,1:36:59.64,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你待会打过去还是我来打 \NYou want to call through later you want me to
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.75,1:37:01.63,2,NTP,0,0,0,,-我会的 谢谢 \N-I'll talk to him,thanks
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.32,1:37:06.73,2,NTP,0,0,0,,-不客气\N-you got it
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.16,1:37:17.25,2,NTP,0,0,0,,卡 太棒了 太棒了\NCut…Beautiful,beautiful,beautiful
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.35,1:37:18.74,2,NTP,0,0,0,,检查摄像机胶片门\NChecking the gate
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.31,1:37:25.35,2,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好 非常好\NBeautifuly done,beautifuly done…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.91,1:37:34.12,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Betsy这是大家送给你的 \NBetsy,we all wanted to give you this
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.21,1:37:37.22,2,NTP,0,0,0,,-天哪\N-oh,my god
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.78,1:37:52.48,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Betsy干得不错\NNice job,Betsy…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.59,1:37:56.21,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得 大家对你真挚的情感都凝结在我这句留言里了\NAnd I think our heartfelt sentiment is echoed in what I wrote
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.30,1:37:58.08,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对会泡这个妹子\NI would totally do her
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.44,1:38:02.03,2,NTP,0,0,0,,完全表达了我的感情\NIt says it all
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.93,1:38:05.52,2,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢大家\NThank you so much
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.63,1:38:10.29,2,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你六年前给我这个机会 我说真的\NI thank you for taking a chance on me six years ago,and I so mean it
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.38,1:38:14.87,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我演员生涯 当然也是我人生中一段重要的经历\NLike it's been such an experience of certainly my career but also my life
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.99,1:38:19.65,2,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你们共事是一段美妙的时光\NJust working with all of you it has just been so wonderful
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.75,1:38:20.90,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我会想念你们的\NI'm gonna miss you all
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.01,1:38:24.80,2,NTP,0,0,0,,大家非常幸运能认识你 上帝保佑你\NWe're all so lucky to know you,we're so lucky to know you,god bless you
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.55,1:38:27.66,2,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起非常开心\NIt's been so much fun
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.75,1:38:30.26,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能给我个结结实实的拥抱吗 \NWill you give me a real hug
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.90,1:38:35.76,2,NTP,0,0,0,,狠狠地抱一下 啊啊啊啊 \NSqueeze me hard ahhhhhhhhhhhh
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.35,1:38:42.83,2,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你想 当然可以 这么多年了\NI can do this,I can do this,if you want me,all these years
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.05,1:38:52.51,2,NTP,0,0,0,,广受好评的电视剧《绝命毒师》在将进入最终季时传出了坏消息\NBad news for TV's most critically acclaimed series Breaking Bad as it heads into its final season
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.60,1:38:55.98,2,NTP,0,0,0,,因Walter White这一角色而广受赞誉的主演Bryan Cranston\NActor Bryan Cranston renowned for his portray of Walter White on the show
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.07,1:38:57.95,2,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚经历了一起入侵盗窃事件\NHas reported a breaking-in incident
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.05,1:39:02.26,2,NTP,0,0,0,,有人从他的车内偷走了一集或甚至两集 机密的《绝命毒师》剧本\NIn which one and possibly even two top secret scripts have been stolen from his car
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.59,1:39:08.24,2,NTP,0,0,0,,反正对宣传有好处 天哪 这太让人惊讶了\NNo such thing is bad for publicity,my god,it's amazing
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.33,1:39:10.08,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我的车被非法闯入了  \NYou know my car was broken into
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.17,1:39:13.17,2,NTP,0,0,0,,有人偷走了我的包 那里面有剧本\NThey snatched my bag with the scripts in it
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.25,1:39:15.08,2,NTP,0,0,0,,现在好像就是炸开了锅\NNow,it's like blown up
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.15,1:39:18.80,2,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密是不是泄露了 最后究竟会发生什么 \NIs the secret going to be released  what's going to happen
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.90,1:39:21.90,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这些采访...你们得看看这个 简直是....\NThe interviews,you've got to see this,it's just...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.98,1:39:24.60,2,NTP,0,0,0,,很大程度上闹得沸沸扬扬\NIt's been blown up to a large proportion
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.26,1:39:27.47,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是最后一集的剧本\NIt was not the final episode,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.44,1:39:32.35,2,NTP,0,0,0,,所以还好 我们没泄密\NSo that's OK,we're safe from that
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.45,1:39:35.40,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们刚得到了揭露911事件真相的录像 敬请期待不要走开\NWe have the 911 tapes,stay tuned
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.27,1:39:39.88,2,NTP,0,0,0,,令人震惊的最新发现\NYou're not going to believe,we just found out,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.04,1:39:56.72,2,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是RJ的最后一天 Walter Jr.的最后一天\NSo this is RJ mite's last day on the series,this is the last day for Walter junior
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.51,1:39:59.76,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在复合公寓群这里拍摄\NAnd we're shooting here at an apartment complex
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.86,1:40:02.90,2,NTP,0,0,0,,在最后一集 这里是非常重要的场景\NThat plays a very major part in the last episode
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.99,1:40:07.58,2,NTP,0,0,0,,拍完最后的镜头 我们就要跟RJ说再见了 会很伤感的 \NIt's gonna be sad we'll finally get the last shot and to say goodbye to RJ
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.56,1:40:13.87,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗 -天哪\NHow are you doing -oh my god
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.95,1:40:15.26,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你身体能往前倾一点吗\NCan you lean forward little bit
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.36,1:40:19.18,2,NTP,0,0,0,,首播集里面Melissa Bernstein就坐在校车里\NMelissa Bernstein was in the school bus in the pilot
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.26,1:40:23.03,2,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在到了全剧的最后一集\NAnd this being the last of the...the last episode of the series
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.11,1:40:25.79,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Melissa要重新回到校车上 所以我们正在布置她坐的位置\NMelisa is once again on the bus,so we're trying to position her
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.88,1:40:28.05,2,NTP,0,0,0,,RJ上车的时候我们就能看见她了\NSo we can see her on the bus when RJ gets on
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.16,1:40:30.85,2,NTP,0,0,0,,第三个垫子了 -是第四个 已经垫了四个垫子了\NThird pad -I'm on the fourth…I'm on four pads
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.12,1:40:33.95,2,NTP,0,0,0,,四个垫子 -现在到第五个了 \NFour pads -this is five
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.63,1:40:37.00,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都看看 这太夸张了\NJust so you know,this is ridiculous
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.09,1:40:40.59,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Melissa Bernstein是个杰出的制片人\NMelissa Bernstein was the most phenomenal producer
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.67,1:40:43.71,2,NTP,0,0,0,,全体演职人员都是这样认为的\NAnd across the board,the cast and crew feel that way
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.82,1:40:45.29,2,NTP,0,0,0,,和她一起工作是件高兴的事\NIt's a pleasure working with her
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.38,1:40:48.86,2,NTP,0,0,0,,她能做本剧的制片人我们非常幸运\NAnd we're so lucky that she's the producer on the show
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.96,1:40:50.05,2,NTP,0,0,0,,从一开始她就参与我们的工作了\NShe's been here from the beginning
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.14,1:40:53.99,2,NTP,0,0,0,,她总有一天会主宰我们这个行业的\NAnd she's going to run this town someday
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.08,1:40:55.24,2,NTP,0,0,0,,她真的棒极了\NI mean she is amazing
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.33,1:41:00.53,2,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里开始就哪里结束 一个循环 从校车开始 -到校车结束\NIt ends where it began,full circle,school buses -school buses
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.61,1:41:01.47,2,NTP,0,0,0,,开拍\NAction
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.21,1:41:10.18,2,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一集的剧情会让你像产生过敏反应一样难受 真的是那样\NThe last episode of Breaking Bad is an allergy,really
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.27,1:41:15.23,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会看到Walt的行为带来的那些 苦楚的血腥的后果\NWe see all the sadness,all the carnage that Walter White's actions have brought
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.33,1:41:22.00,2,NTP,0,0,0,,而这些后果 我认为最明显地体现在Walt Jr和Holly的身上\NAnd we see that I think that most clearly in the persons of Walter Jr. And Holly
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.11,1:41:27.13,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你能想象吗 失去了你的父亲 失去了你的家\NCan you imagine losing your father,losing your house
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.20,1:41:29.42,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你曾拥有的一切化为乌有\NLosing everything that you've ever had
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.50,1:41:31.48,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你整个人生都被毁掉了\NYour whole life was destroyed
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.54,1:41:34.13,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是这部剧里的无辜者\NThey are the innocence of the show
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.21,1:41:40.00,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这两个孩子很好地概括了这部剧所有受害者的形象\NI think all of the victims are probably pretty well summed up in the persons of these two children
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.67,1:41:47.10,2,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 卡 非常好\NAlright,cut,very nice -cutting
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.71,1:41:49.86,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Mitte先生 请问你能过来一下吗 -什么\NMr. Mitte,come here,please -yes
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.96,1:41:54.35,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吗 -我想说非常感谢 -谢谢你\NHow are you -I wanted to say thank you so much -thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.43,1:41:55.77,2,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你选择在我们剧组长大成人 \NFor growing up on our set
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.95,1:42:00.90,2,NTP,0,0,0,,成为那么优秀的年轻演员 做出那么出色的工作\NAnd become such a fine young actor and doing such a great great work
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.00,1:42:02.26,2,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝保佑你 \NGod bless you man
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.34,1:42:04.68,2,NTP,0,0,0,,六年来你的工作十分出色\NYou did wonderful job for six years now
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.15,1:42:16.45,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想给你开个支票 -耶\NWe would like to hand you this check -yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.21,1:42:19.09,2,NTP,0,0,0,,哪家银行会给我兑啊\NWho would accept it
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.95,1:42:22.15,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿着这个随便到哪家银行都能拿到钱\NYou take that to any bank build up,cash up
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.01,1:42:24.50,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没在这个上面留言呢 -你还没呢 \NI haven't sign this one yet -you haven't
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.59,1:42:26.26,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上给你写 不过没有记号笔\NIt'll get signed,but I haven't got a sharpie
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.35,1:42:28.04,2,NTP,0,0,0,,谁过来帮个忙 好了\N-somebody get over here,there we are
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.13,1:42:29.60,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就知道我们能保持良好状态\NI knew we were gonna in good shape
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.70,1:42:36.20,2,NTP,0,0,0,,在首播集服装店的那场戏里 Anna抛出来一句即兴台词\NIn the pilot when anna threw out an ad-lib in the clothing store scene
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.30,1:42:38.35,2,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他在试牛仔裤的时候 \NWhen he's trying on the jeans,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.44,1:42:41.09,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你说 这裤子感觉很有轮滑风格\NAnd you said yeah,just like a skater's wear
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.17,1:42:44.17,2,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你就顺势接下来 我看起来像是个会溜冰的么\NAnd you threw it back,do I look like a skater to you
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.26,1:42:46.63,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我那时就想 这以后可该有意思了\NI was like it's gonna be fun
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.16,1:42:50.97,2,NTP,0,0,0,,致: 荧幕上最失败父亲的好儿子\NTo the best son of television's worst father
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.06,1:42:55.36,2,NTP,0,0,0,,致: 荧幕上最失败父亲暨绝命债主的好儿子 \NTo the best son of television's worst father you can never owe for
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.53,1:42:57.57,2,NTP,0,0,0,,碉堡了\NThat is awesome
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.96,1:43:08.54,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个棒极了的人 我爱你\NYou're a great great great person,I love you
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.65,1:43:10.09,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你\NI love you too
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.49,1:43:21.18,2,NTP,0,0,0,,就绪 就绪 开拍\NSet,set and action
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.26,1:43:24.46,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Bryan和我拍了我们在一起的最后一场戏\NBryan and I did our last scene together and
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.57,1:43:30.54,2,NTP,0,0,0,,绝妙的是我们能够以角色的身份来互相告别\NIt was so wonderful because in a way we got to say goodbye to each other as characters
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.24,1:43:33.43,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我做的那些事\NThe things that I did
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.94,1:43:37.21,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你得明白我为什么做了它们\NYou need to understand why I did them
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.31,1:43:46.46,2,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 你要是再敢说一遍你是为了这个家\NOh god,if you say one more time that you did this for the family…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.52,1:43:48.83,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为我自己\NI did it for me
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.08,1:43:55.97,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是这场六年情感波折的结束了\NThis is the end of a six-year,very emotional roller-coaster
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.06,1:44:01.21,2,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着很费力 你就能想象这种心境\NAnd…So it didn't take much to be able to conjure up
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.30,1:44:05.62,2,NTP,0,0,0,,要知道 在这样一种很动情的环境下你很容易进入角色\NYou know in an emotional state that put you in the right frame of mind
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.72,1:44:13.57,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我能看看她吗  求你了..\NMay I see her please…
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.69,1:44:19.41,2,NTP,0,0,0,,卡 棒极了\NAnd cut,awesome
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.75,1:44:28.09,2,NTP,0,0,0,,后来在育婴室里 我们经历了一段小小的宁静时刻\NAnd then we had that little peace in the nursery afterwards
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.18,1:44:31.58,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那感觉太棒了\NAnd it was amazing
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.67,1:44:34.75,2,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小宝宝的原因 我们必须保持完全安静\NBecause we bad to be totally silent because of the baby
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.83,1:44:38.42,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那是第一次 小宝宝必须真正睡着的场景\NThat's the first time the baby was actually sleeping
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.53,1:44:45.57,2,NTP,0,0,0,,整个片场都被一种宁静温和的气氛笼罩了\NIt put this through a feel over the entire set of this calm,sort of placid
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.68,1:44:50.39,2,NTP,0,0,0,,美好又安静 有点禅的意味在里头\NSort of beautiful,the zen thing
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.48,1:44:52.56,2,NTP,0,0,0,,一度我和Bryan甚至提出来\NYou know,and Bryan and I actually said at one point
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.64,1:44:55.28,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们真该一直都这样做\NWe should do it like this all the time
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.13,1:45:01.48,2,NTP,0,0,0,,-就绪 -就绪 -开拍\N-set -set -action
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.27,1:45:07.43,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我正看着我的女儿\NAs I'm looking at my daughter
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.53,1:45:08.77,2,NTP,0,0,0,,全身都充满了情感\NAnd I'm filled with emotion
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.86,1:45:10.70,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须要跟她告别了\NI have to now say goodbye
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.79,1:45:14.18,2,NTP,0,0,0,,其实演那场戏时我本来准备不流眼泪的\NAnd I actually meant to play that scene without tears
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.31,1:45:17.39,2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我感情上真的没有准备好\NBut I was just not emotionally prepared for that
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.47,1:45:20.03,2,NTP,0,0,0,,因为周遭发生的一切对我的影响太大了\NBecause of the impact of everything that was going on
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.14,1:45:24.56,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的摄影师Andy 在肩膀上扛着摄像机\NAndy Voegeli,who is our camera operator,he's got this camera on his shoulder
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.65,1:45:28.25,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他离我只有这么远了 因为他想近距离拍摄\NAnd he is this far away from me,because you wanna get close
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.33,1:45:30.33,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我看着我的女儿\NAnd as I'm looking at my daughter
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.42,1:45:34.29,2,NTP,0,0,0,,同时可以听到刚荣升为爸爸的Andy\NI can hear Andy,who's a relatively new father
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.13,1:45:40.21,2,NTP,0,0,0,,正在镜头后哭泣 \NHe's crying behind the camera
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.29,1:45:42.74,2,NTP,0,0,0,,并仍旧努力保持静止不动 稳住摄像机\NAnd trying to be still holding the camera
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.62,1:45:44.71,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那是很动情的一场戏 \NIt was a very emotional scene
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.80,1:45:48.01,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我透过目镜看的时候泪流不止\NI got teared up looking through the eyepiece
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.11,1:45:53.02,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道 我确信当时我发出来了一些抽泣的声音\NYou know,I'm sure there were some audible sighs and snuffs coming ahead of me
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.73,1:45:56.07,2,NTP,0,0,0,,剧组人员也是一样悲伤 \NThe crew as well
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.17,1:45:58.79,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在说再见 欢乐时光要结束了\NWe are saying goodbye,it was the end of run
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.21,1:46:02.42,2,NTP,0,0,0,,很真诚的情感都自然流露了出来\NAnd honest emotions were coming out
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.17,1:46:08.95,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我熬过了剩下的一天 但是当Aaron出现时\NI got through the rest of the day and then when Aaron showed up
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.04,1:46:10.87,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我突然承受不了了\NThen I was just,that was it for me
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.96,1:46:12.78,2,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子感受到了分别的真实感\NI was just,that just killed me
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.68,1:46:20.36,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我突然意识到将要结束的这一现实\NIt was,I think then was the realization was hitting me that
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.44,1:46:25.70,2,NTP,0,0,0,,短短数分钟内 寥寥几次拍摄以后\NIn a number of,in a matter of takes,in a matter of minutes
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.79,1:46:27.54,2,NTP,0,0,0,,就真真正正结束了\NIt was really going to be over
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.80,1:46:39.61,2,NTP,0,0,0,,卡\NCutting
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.97,1:46:43.52,2,NTP,0,0,0,,检查摄像机胶片口\NCheck the gate
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.01,1:46:50.61,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拍摄了Anna在《绝命毒师》的最后一场戏\NWe got the scene and that was anna's last shot on Breaking Bad
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.01,1:46:57.30,2,NTP,0,0,0,,马上整个房间都充满了悲伤的情绪\NAnd it became a very emotional room very quickly
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.42,1:47:00.80,2,NTP,0,0,0,,当我们最后拍完Anna的那场戏以后\NWhen we finish shooting that final scene with anna
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.90,1:47:03.97,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的副导演将我们转移到舞台一角\NOur assistant director moved us over to a different part of the stage
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.08,1:47:08.61,2,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们都可以聚在一起享受最后一刻\NSo that we could all gather together and enjoy that last moment
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.72,1:47:16.08,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Anna最后那番再见和谢谢的演说非常感人 触动人心\NAnd anna gave an incredibly heart-felt,touching goodbye and thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.26,1:47:22.70,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉就好像..和艺术家们 和朋友们一起在进行着艺术创作\NIt's felt like,like I said,it's felt like making art with artists,with friends
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.61,1:47:27.65,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远都会心怀感激的 非常感谢你们所有人\NAnd I'm forever grateful and I thank you all so much
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.77,1:47:31.57,2,NTP,0,0,0,,-我爱你们 我会想你们的 -我们也爱你\N-I love you,I'll miss you -we love you too
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.92,1:47:41.55,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Anna演的这个角色 像我说的 是个很难把握的角色\NAnna playing that character and a tough role to hold as I say
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.64,1:47:43.69,2,NTP,0,0,0,,而她演的却相当好\NAnd she credited herself beautifully
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.78,1:47:45.27,2,NTP,0,0,0,,她是一个非凡的演员\NShe is a marvelous actor
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.35,1:47:49.23,2,NTP,0,0,0,,演的角色难度很高 还有点吃力不讨好\NPlaying a very hard,at times somewhat thankless part
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.78,1:47:53.18,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我没法想象还有其他人能比她做得更好\NAnd I can't picture anybody doing better
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.95,1:48:02.14,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 Jack 你在家吗 \NHello,jack,are you home
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.84,1:48:05.24,2,NTP,0,0,0,,人家想跟你聊聊天 你现在有空吗\NJack,I want to talk to you for a second,you got a minute
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.91,1:48:09.38,2,NTP,0,0,0,,-有兴趣买一架我做的发射器吗 -当然\N-can I interest you in the launch tower -yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.36,1:48:12.45,2,NTP,0,0,0,,开拍\NAnd action
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.50,1:48:17.37,2,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪 看看你那乱蓬蓬的一头头发\NJesus,look at you with that head of hair
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.48,1:48:18.56,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那是真的吗\NIs that real
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.19,1:48:20.14,2,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\NYes
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.89,1:48:22.44,2,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一个假发  你来真的 \NThat's not a wig seriously
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.92,1:48:26.16,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前怎么光头呢 故意剃的吗\NWhat were you doing before,shaving it
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.92,1:48:28.42,2,NTP,0,0,0,,恩\NYes
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.45,1:48:31.33,2,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝啊 那可是一头好发\NChrist,that is one fine head of hair
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.41,1:48:33.86,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说 没了它你看上去像坨屎\NI mean,otherwise you look like shit,but...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.72,1:48:36.83,2,NTP,0,0,0,,也向你问好 Jack\NHello to you too,jack
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.92,1:48:38.61,2,NTP,0,0,0,,希望一切准备就绪之后\NHopefully when it's all setting down
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.70,1:48:41.79,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这会成为一个无比精彩 激动人心的 戏剧化的场景\NIt's gonna be a tremendously thrilling,exciting,dramatic scene
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.87,1:48:45.80,2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在这个纳粹俱乐部的布景里拍摄 我感觉在像地狱一样\NBut shooting inside this nazi clubhouse set was like hell
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.89,1:48:48.76,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌它 每一分钟都讨厌\NI hated it,just like the every minute of it
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.99,1:48:54.80,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你能听到我吗\NDo you hear me
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.46,1:48:56.92,2,NTP,0,0,0,,停 很好\NCut,very nice
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.57,1:49:00.48,2,NTP,0,0,0,,片场像是让你得了幽闭恐惧症一般压抑\NIt got very claustrophobic in the set
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.59,1:49:03.86,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那里感觉非常紧张 非常昏暗 常常烟雾缭绕\NIt was very tight,it was very dark,it was often filled with smoke
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.94,1:49:06.06,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你晚上擤鼻子的时候\NYou blow your nose at the end of the night
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.13,1:49:08.37,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFF00&\pos(313,28)}Rorschach Blot:罗夏墨迹测验  
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.13,1:49:08.37,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那鼻涕就像墨汁一样的\NAnd it comes out looking like a {\c&HFFFF00&}Rorschach blot
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.46,1:49:10.76,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你就会想 这种日子什么时候才是个头啊\NYou know,and you are a little like uh,when will this end
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.85,1:49:13.71,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这是痛苦的折磨 我等不及它结束了\NThis is agony,I couldn't wait for it to be over
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.32,1:49:17.61,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切得以顺利进行 还是因为那些伟大的演员\NWhat made it do-able was because the great actors that we had
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.68,1:49:19.00,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有Bryan 和Aaron \NWe had Bryan and Aaron
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.07,1:49:21.54,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有纳粹一伙和Jack大叔\NAnd we had the nazis,we had uncle jack
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.64,1:49:24.13,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有Kenny和Todd\NWe had Kenny and we had Todd
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.24,1:49:26.35,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是最可爱的纳粹组合了\NThose are the most lovable bunch of nazis
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.44,1:49:29.03,2,NTP,0,0,0,,任何人能与他们共事都很幸运\NAnyone's ever had the privilege spending time with
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.12,1:49:31.35,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我是开玩笑的 我是说这些演员\NI'm joking,but I mean the actors
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.43,1:49:34.17,2,NTP,0,0,0,,和他们一起共事非常愉快\NWho play the roles were a pleasure to work with
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.26,1:49:35.36,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他们让这个过程变得好受些了\NAnd they made it easier
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.15,1:49:40.24,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我在说什么吗 你个狗娘养的\NYou see what I'm talking about,you son of a bitch
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.16,1:49:49.13,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你看这像个搭档的样子么\NThis look like a partner to you
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.80,1:49:55.80,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Walt有很好的理由去对Jesse发火 痛恨Jesse\NWalt has in his mind,good reason to be furious at Jesse,to hate Jesse
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.47,1:49:57.78,2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是最后一刻 \NBut in that final moment
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.84,1:49:59.55,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他还是没法扣动扳机杀了他\NHe can't pull the trigger on him
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.67,1:50:07.46,2,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了 太棒了\NOh,man -ah,wonderful wonderful
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.01,1:50:09.90,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Aaron 你想尝试下别的方法吗\NAaron,anything else you'd like to try
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.63,1:50:12.29,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是在给你下套子\NNot a trick question
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.02,1:50:15.63,2,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 这个再试试看\NAh yeah let's try this one more
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.81,1:50:19.36,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你拍戏的时候一直承受着这样的压力\NYou have that pressure behind you the whole time you are shooting
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.44,1:50:22.08,2,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他方法吗  有没有什么东西被我们遗漏了 \NLike is there anything else is there something we are missing
Dialogue: 0,1:50:22.16,1:50:24.91,2,NTP,0,0,0,,细节处理得怎么样 有什么细微的差别吗 \NWhat are the details any nuances anything
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.00,1:50:26.72,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你想试试别的东西吗  有什么其他的想法吗  \NYou wanna try something any idea
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.79,1:50:29.10,2,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在进行着这种思考\NYou know,constantly doing them
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.19,1:50:32.38,2,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 我就好像 不敢看着他\NAnd then,I'm like can't look at him
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.57,1:50:37.62,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他很害怕...\NHe's like scared and just...
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.52,1:50:43.59,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那种愤怒呢 那种肌肉反应\NWhat's it like ..the anger...the muscle memory
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.65,1:50:46.78,2,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就...你甚至发起抖了\NThen it's like...even it vibrates
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.88,1:50:48.34,2,NTP,0,0,0,,行 我们开始吧 很棒\NAll right let's do it,excellent
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.08,1:50:52.45,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会因为好像少了点什么就让他们再多拍一次\NI'm not saying do one one more because I feel there's something lacking
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.56,1:50:56.01,2,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是我们最后一场戏了\NJust because this is our last go-round
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.11,1:50:58.14,2,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我希望他们能像我一样开心\NAnd I wanted them to be as happy as I can be
Dialogue: 0,1:50:58.24,1:51:00.29,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴他多拍了一次\NI'm so glad he took that extra take
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.37,1:51:02.87,2,NTP,0,0,0,,因为即使之前那条拍的已经很不错了 他愿意再拍一遍\NBecause he took it,as deep as the previous take was
