Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.74,2:00:24.08,2,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是不够高\NThat still don't go high enough
Dialogue: 0,2:00:24.17,2:00:27.97,2,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们把这个巨大的吊车放在了脚手架上面\NSo we put the giant technic crane on top of the giant scaffolding
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.06,2:00:29.29,2,NTP,0,0,0,,达到需求的高度\N To get high enough up
Dialogue: 0,2:00:29.38,2:00:34.31,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是Walt咽下最后一口气的地方\NAnd this is going to be where Walt takes his final breath
Dialogue: 0,2:00:35.16,2:00:37.23,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你能把眼睛睁到多大 能再大一点吗\NHow wide you opened your eyes pretty much a little bit
Dialogue: 0,2:00:37.30,2:00:40.95,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以再睁大一点 -实际上我觉得...\NYou know I can open it up a little wider -I don't know...actually I
Dialogue: 0,2:00:43.79,2:00:45.87,2,NTP,0,0,0,,对 你现在这样就很好了\NYeah,actually what you are doing right now was pretty good
Dialogue: 0,2:00:47.21,2:00:51.03,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让他死时的神情有种模棱两可的感觉\NI wanna maintain an ambiguity about his look
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.39,2:00:55.02,2,NTP,0,0,0,,-他的眼睛是闭上的吗 -睁开的 -是吗\N-will his eyes be closed -open -they'll be open
Dialogue: 0,2:00:55.12,2:00:56.16,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之前谈过这点\NWe talked about that too
Dialogue: 0,2:00:56.25,2:01:00.51,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我们需要这样做 眼睛得睁开\NI just think we deserve it…We need to have it open
Dialogue: 0,2:01:00.60,2:01:04.54,2,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛闭着的话 好像是说他释然了\NWhen eyes are closed,there's more sense that he's at peace
Dialogue: 0,2:01:04.62,2:01:08.88,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不想传达非黑即白的意义\NAnd I don't really want to convey one thing or the other
Dialogue: 0,2:01:08.96,2:01:11.82,2,NTP,0,0,0,,就绪-就绪 -开拍\NSet -set -and action
Dialogue: 0,2:01:13.49,2:01:16.21,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不仅仅探讨Walt带来的外在的危险\NWe explored not only the physical danger what
Dialogue: 0,2:01:16.30,2:01:20.61,2,NTP,0,0,0,,包括他带给他自己的 他的家人还有他的朋友的\NWalt has subjected to himself and his family and his friends too
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.71,2:01:22.99,2,NTP,0,0,0,,还有情感上的危险  \NBut the emotional danger
Dialogue: 0,2:01:23.07,2:01:24.93,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他作为一个自然人来说遭遇了什么\NWhat has happened to him as a human being
Dialogue: 0,2:01:25.88,2:01:28.02,2,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂的堕落 \NDegradation of his soul
Dialogue: 0,2:01:28.12,2:01:32.57,2,NTP,0,0,0,,自我的膨胀\NThe inclusion of ego and hubris
Dialogue: 0,2:01:32.67,2:01:37.87,2,NTP,0,0,0,,从未有过的坏的特质在他身上出现了\NHe developed an adverse nature which he never had before
Dialogue: 0,2:01:39.23,2:01:43.29,2,NTP,0,0,0,,于是将这些负面的情感特质融入了进来\NSo those kind of negative emotional traits played in
Dialogue: 0,2:01:44.16,2:01:45.27,2,NTP,0,0,0,,行动\NMove…
Dialogue: 0,2:01:48.13,2:01:51.48,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我想最后一刻还有一丝胜利的意味\NI think there's an element of victory to be hung here
Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.56,2:01:53.63,2,NTP,0,0,0,,它很微妙 但确实在那\NIt's subtle but it's there
Dialogue: 0,2:01:54.38,2:01:57.36,2,NTP,0,0,0,,结局恰如其时 又如他所愿\NHe ended things the moment he wanted to end them,on his own terms
Dialogue: 0,2:01:57.46,2:02:02.58,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得 他对于自己的犯下的种种罪孽后悔不已\NI think he has got a great many regrets on a great great many sins under his belt
Dialogue: 0,2:02:02.68,2:02:05.31,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那些让他愧疚的事 那些他希望从未发生的事 \NThings he was sorry for,things he wished he never done
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.39,2:02:09.04,2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那时已经没有后悔药可以吃 没有回头路可以走了\NBut there's no going back and doing them at that point
Dialogue: 0,2:02:10.05,2:02:12.42,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他能做的就是把这些恩怨给了结了\NAll this guy left to do is take care of his business
Dialogue: 0,2:02:12.50,2:02:15.87,2,NTP,0,0,0,,然后把剩下的钱给他的妻儿\NAnd gave his remaining money to his children and his wife
Dialogue: 0,2:02:15.95,2:02:18.62,2,NTP,0,0,0,,最后 像个牛逼闪闪的大坏蛋一样死去\NAnd then,gone like a god-damn man
Dialogue: 0,2:02:18.72,2:02:20.21,2,NTP,0,0,0,,而这就是他所做的\NAnd that was what he does
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.19,2:02:24.85,2,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 卡 非常棒\NAlright,cut…Very good -cutting
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.43,2:02:28.46,2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(328,30)} {\c&HFFFF00&}APD：Albuquerque Police Department
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.43,2:02:28.46,2,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢你们 Albuquerque警察局的同志们 \NThank you very much to the {\c&HFFFF00&}APD
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.54,2:02:30.26,2,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮\NWell done APD
Dialogue: 0,2:02:36.19,2:02:37.66,2,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的表现都很好哦\NGood job everybody
Dialogue: 0,2:02:42.59,2:02:45.22,2,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们 来击个爪 来\NThank you…Bong…Bong…
Dialogue: 0,2:02:51.14,2:02:54.71,2,NTP,0,0,0,,全剧最后摄制日:第五季第十四集 奥西曼提斯 引子
Dialogue: 0,2:02:54.82,2:02:57.17,2,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一天了\NIt's the last day
Dialogue: 0,2:03:01.68,2:03:02.91,2,NTP,0,0,0,,看看我们勇敢无畏的头头\NOur fearless leader
Dialogue: 0,2:03:06.39,2:03:07.93,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始难过了\NI'm starting to get very sad
Dialogue: 0,2:03:08.03,2:03:11.09,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这是《绝命毒师》拍摄的最后一天\NThis is the last day ever of Breaking Bad
Dialogue: 0,2:03:11.17,2:03:17.37,2,NTP,0,0,0,,可能一个小时后就能杀青了 可能还会更快\NIt's gonna be series wrapped probably within the next hour,if not sooner
Dialogue: 0,2:03:17.46,2:03:20.28,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉到真的是要结束了 我开始有点...\NAnd it's starting to hit me I'm starting to get ...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:26.11,2:03:28.63,2,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人为这部剧即将结束而开心\NNobody's happy about finishing the show
Dialogue: 0,2:03:28.71,2:03:30.59,2,NTP,0,0,0,,因为大家都那么在意彼此\NBecause we all care for each other so much
Dialogue: 0,2:03:30.67,2:03:32.34,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为我们的工作而自豪\NAnd we are so proud of the work
Dialogue: 0,2:03:32.43,2:03:34.43,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们热爱这些角色 我们热爱这个故事\NAnd we love these characters,and we love the story
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.52,2:03:36.66,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们将在这个特定的地方结束拍摄\NBut the fact that we are doing it here
Dialogue: 0,2:03:36.75,2:03:42.31,2,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我们拍摄的是首播集的闪回情节\NAnd the fact that we are ending with this flashback moment where we get to leap back to the pilot
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.42,2:03:46.49,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这两件事从我的创作角度 以及我的情感角度上来看\NFrom my creative standpoint,and sort of a sentimental standpoint
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.57,2:03:48.18,2,NTP,0,0,0,,都是非常美妙的\NIs really wonderful
Dialogue: 0,2:03:48.26,2:03:52.52,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想或许这周末我们全家可以聚一聚\NI was thinking that maybe we can have a little family time this weekend
Dialogue: 0,2:03:52.62,2:03:58.20,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这个场景直到今天才拍摄 是出于很实际的原因\NThere was a pragmatic reason for us to be here on this last day,where we started this
Dialogue: 0,2:03:58.30,2:04:01.88,2,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我和Aaron的胡子\NAnd that was,our beards
Dialogue: 0,2:04:02.82,2:04:06.30,2,NTP,0,0,0,,很显然 我肯定得把胡子剃了才能拍这一部分\NSo,obviously I couldn't have a beard to shoot this segment
Dialogue: 0,2:04:07.45,2:04:13.41,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得太幸运了 能够执导这一集我感到很荣幸\NI felt just beyond lucky,I felt privileged just be able to be doing this episode
Dialogue: 0,2:04:14.38,2:04:17.83,2,NTP,0,0,0,,因为Walt和Jesse看起来像在试播集里一样\NBecause Walt and Jesse look like they did in the pilot
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.72,2:04:24.89,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道怎么说 我觉得我真的很幸运\NI don't know man,I feel pretty damn privileged
Dialogue: 0,2:04:25.69,2:04:27.08,2,NTP,0,0,0,,-先生们 他们准备好了 \NGentlemen,they are ready for you
Dialogue: 0,2:04:28.60,2:04:29.89,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有准备好\NOh,I'm not ready for them
Dialogue: 0,2:04:31.68,2:04:32.83,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我没准备好\NI'm not ready
Dialogue: 0,2:04:32.93,2:04:37.53,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Aaron只是在用这些失落的碎碎念来开玩笑\NAaron was just mucking around with a mantra of depression
Dialogue: 0,2:04:37.64,2:04:42.34,2,NTP,0,0,0,,嗷..嗷..嗷.. 额 我天\NOh.no...oh..Jesus
Dialogue: 0,2:04:43.02,2:04:50.36,2,NTP,0,0,0,,比如这太可怕了 这太糟糕了 然后还露出这种表情\NLike,this is horrible,this is awful and he looked like this
Dialogue: 0,2:04:55.62,2:05:02.54,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他很可爱 不至于说是天真无邪 但是从我们相遇 他就如此可爱\NHe was as sweet and,not quite as innocent but as sweet as the day we started
Dialogue: 0,2:05:02.65,2:05:04.74,2,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好难过\NOh,this is terrible
Dialogue: 0,2:05:04.85,2:05:07.86,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备好退出了吗 我想可能是的\NAm I ready to hang up these cleats I guess so
Dialogue: 0,2:05:07.94,2:05:12.78,2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很明显我已经对Jesse Pinkman 这个角色产生了个人情感\NBut obviously I have a such personal relationship with Jesse Pinkman
Dialogue: 0,2:05:13.66,2:05:15.56,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常喜欢他\NAnd I love him dearly
Dialogue: 0,2:05:16.40,2:05:21.51,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我很难过我再也不能演Jesse了\NAnd it's sad to me that I will never play Jesse Pinkman again
Dialogue: 0,2:05:25.11,2:05:28.02,2,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 接下来要做什么\NYo,so what's next
Dialogue: 0,2:05:28.86,2:05:30.07,2,NTP,0,0,0,,等\NWe wait
Dialogue: 0,2:05:31.02,2:05:35.16,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是应该还有八件屁事要去做吗\NDon't we have like 8 more anal things to check
Dialogue: 0,2:05:35.73,2:05:40.38,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Aaron是个非常感性的人 是个情感外露的人\NAaron is somebody who is so emotional,absolutely heart on his sleeve
Dialogue: 0,2:05:40.48,2:05:44.72,2,NTP,0,0,0,,感知能力很迅速很深入\NAnd who feels things very immediately and very deeply
Dialogue: 0,2:05:44.80,2:05:51.17,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得Bryan作为他的依靠 能帮助Aaron过完这最后一天\NAnd I think it's gonna help Aaron quite a bit to get through the day having Bryan as an anchor
Dialogue: 0,2:05:51.27,2:05:55.47,2,NTP,0,0,0,,卡 核对中... -爱死这段了\NCutting,checking -love it
Dialogue: 0,2:05:55.58,2:05:57.63,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们转过去再拍\NAnd we will turn around
Dialogue: 0,2:05:57.70,2:06:01.98,2,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得我这大师级的特写镜头咋样啊  哈哈 顺便说一句 我得走了\NHow's my master close-up  haha,by the way I have to go
Dialogue: 0,2:06:03.74,2:06:06.05,2,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的能让Sean上来演吗 \NCan we get sean in here to do the thing
Dialogue: 0,2:06:06.13,2:06:07.80,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的想上路回家了\NI'd really like to get on the road
Dialogue: 0,2:06:07.87,2:06:11.54,2,NTP,0,0,0,,避开交通拥挤什么的...那就太好了\NYou know,beat the traffic and everything  that'd be great
Dialogue: 0,2:06:11.63,2:06:13.34,2,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁反对吗  \NAnybody have an objection to that
Dialogue: 0,2:06:13.41,2:06:16.47,2,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦 大家再见\NOK,good,bye,y'all
Dialogue: 0,2:06:16.56,2:06:20.53,2,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了 你们俩能过来拍吗\N-thanks very much -will you two turn around in here
Dialogue: 0,2:06:21.50,2:06:23.72,2,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一个镜头 Christine \NFinal shot  Christine
Dialogue: 0,2:06:23.80,2:06:26.69,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我是最后一个镜头  我就说嘛\NI'm the last shot  that's what I'm talking about
Dialogue: 0,2:06:29.60,2:06:31.89,2,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊啊  这真是噩梦啊\NAh,it's nightmare
Dialogue: 0,2:06:31.96,2:06:35.25,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Bryan定了基调 他会让你觉得 不用难过啊\NBryan set the tone,that,you know,it's gonna be OK
Dialogue: 0,2:06:35.33,2:06:42.89,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走了那么远 这件事应该是让我们感到开心和荣耀的\NAnd you know it's a long road and this is something to be happy about and to honor
Dialogue: 0,2:06:42.98,2:06:47.96,2,NTP,0,0,0,,保持快乐的心情才是我们这段体验最重要的部分\NBut you know but to really keep the joy at the forefront of this experience
Dialogue: 0,2:06:48.04,2:06:51.33,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他的观点帮助了我们所有人\NAnd I think his perspective helped us all
Dialogue: 0,2:06:51.42,2:06:56.06,2,NTP,0,0,0,,-没事的 -天呐 别看着我\NIt's OK -Jesus don't even look at me
Dialogue: 0,2:07:02.72,2:07:05.97,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们马上要拍《绝命毒师》最后一个镜头了\NWe are about to shoot the very last shot of Breaking Bad
Dialogue: 0,2:07:06.88,2:07:08.74,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我戴着太阳镜是因为我在哭\NI'm wearing sun glasses because I'm crying
Dialogue: 0,2:07:12.68,2:07:14.56,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Rian是这集的导演\NRian Johnson is the director of this episode
Dialogue: 0,2:07:14.68,2:07:17.08,2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他请我为最后一个镜头喊卡\NBut he asked me to call cut for the very final shot
Dialogue: 0,2:07:17.19,2:07:18.31,2,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了\NThere is good
Dialogue: 0,2:07:18.45,2:07:20.51,2,NTP,0,0,0,,来 我们整好你的小内裤 弄一下就好了\NTighty-whity.here we go,just a little
Dialogue: 0,2:07:20.63,2:07:22.22,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感动\NAnd I was very touched by that
Dialogue: 0,2:07:22.30,2:07:26.13,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我那时想说我很期待\NI was about to say that I'm looking forward for doing that
Dialogue: 0,2:07:26.21,2:07:27.93,2,NTP,0,0,0,,但其实并不是 因为当我那样做的时候\NI'm not,because when I do that
Dialogue: 0,2:07:28.01,2:07:31.07,2,NTP,0,0,0,,就意味着正式剧终了 一切都结束了\NIt means it's officially wrapped,it's officially done,put to bed
Dialogue: 0,2:07:31.15,2:07:35.30,2,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那很让人感动 我很期待那一刻 会很好的\NBut that was very sweet,I'm looking forward to doing it,it'll be nice
Dialogue: 0,2:07:37.18,2:07:41.18,2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可能的话 我想再拍一次我们之前拍的那场戏\NI'd like to reshoot that scene we did earlier,if possible
Dialogue: 0,2:07:42.26,2:07:43.92,2,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 图像出来了\NAlright picture is up
Dialogue: 0,2:07:45.43,2:07:50.76,2,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 开拍\NOK -set,action
Dialogue: 0,2:07:51.43,2:07:52.60,2,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们有个冰箱\NWell,if we had a freezer
Dialogue: 0,2:07:52.68,2:07:55.62,2,NTP,0,0,0,,凝结液就会冷却地更快\NThe condensed liquid would cool more quickly
Dialogue: 0,2:07:55.71,2:08:00.52,2,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是个放热反应\NBecause,of course,this is an exothermic reaction
Dialogue: 0,2:08:01.58,2:08:03.37,2,NTP,0,0,0,,意思就是会散发出热量\NWhich means giving heat off
Dialogue: 0,2:08:04.20,2:08:06.71,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你不如打昏了我算了\NPut me into a coma,why don't you
Dialogue: 0,2:08:13.85,2:08:15.84,2,NTP,0,0,0,,别在这里抽\NNot in here
Dialogue: 0,2:08:16.80,2:08:19.29,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么 你做了什么\NWhat do you say,what's happening here
Dialogue: 0,2:08:26.60,2:08:29.23,2,NTP,0,0,0,,-天呐 -你还在拍呢 是吧 -对\N-oh my god -you still rolling right -still rolling
Dialogue: 0,2:08:29.30,2:08:30.66,2,NTP,0,0,0,,美利坚人民可都盼着这个呢\NIt is what America wants
Dialogue: 0,2:08:33.83,2:08:35.22,2,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我们要拍了\NAlright,here we go
Dialogue: 0,2:08:44.39,2:08:45.97,2,NTP,0,0,0,,开拍\NAction
Dialogue: 0,2:08:47.02,2:08:52.02,2,NTP,0,0,0,,-别在这里抽 -你把我当做傻瓜呢\NNot in here -duh. Like I'm an idiot
Dialogue: 0,2:08:53.53,2:08:56.11,2,NTP,0,0,0,,对 你就是我的小傻瓜\NYeah. Like you're an idiot
Dialogue: 0,2:09:02.34,2:09:04.64,2,NTP,0,0,0,,卡\NAnd cut
Dialogue: 0,2:09:14.68,2:09:19.77,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Vince是我作为制片人最引以为豪的发现\NVince is one of my proudest if not my proudest sort of discovery as a producer
Dialogue: 0,2:09:19.86,2:09:24.17,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他拥有非凡独到的见解\NAnd I knew that he had such a special singular voice
Dialogue: 0,2:09:24.26,2:09:28.09,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常为他自豪 难以用言语表达的自豪\NI couldn't be more proud of,I can't tell you how proud I am of him
Dialogue: 0,2:09:28.16,2:09:31.31,2,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢你们 我们就像一个大家庭\NThank you all so much,we're all like a family
Dialogue: 0,2:09:33.52,2:09:36.75,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们马上 好像就要拆散这个大家庭一样\NWow we're gonna like break a family here
Dialogue: 0,2:09:38.89,2:09:41.05,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远不会忘记 这么非凡的经历 \NAnd I'll never forget.this is brilliant
Dialogue: 0,2:09:41.13,2:09:48.81,2,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 谢谢你们每一个人 愿上帝保佑你们\NSo any of you,thank you so much...god bless you
Dialogue: 0,2:09:58.78,2:10:03.34,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们深知自己是如此幸运 \NWe do know how lucky we are,how fortunate we've had
Dialogue: 0,2:10:04.28,2:10:07.79,2,NTP,0,0,0,,能够参与到这个过程中 尤其是能和这个人一起\NTo be on this ride,especially with this man here
Dialogue: 0,2:10:07.89,2:10:15.78,2,NTP,0,0,0,,一个创造了这个独一无二的环境和风格\NWho has created an environment,a style
Dialogue: 0,2:10:15.89,2:10:19.20,2,NTP,0,0,0,,还有独特叙事手法的人\NA storytelling that is so unique
Dialogue: 0,2:10:20.67,2:10:22.73,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都知道这会引起什么样的反应\NAnd it is getting that reaction as we all know
Dialogue: 0,2:10:23.79,2:10:31.40,2,NTP,0,0,0,,他把我们带到这里 不仅仅改变了我的个人生活 职业人生\NHe brought us all here,not only change my life personally,professionally
Dialogue: 0,2:10:31.49,2:10:34.69,2,NTP,0,0,0,,还有Aaron的 还有所有演员所有编剧的人生\NAnd Aaron's and all of the actors' but all the writers' too
Dialogue: 0,2:10:34.77,2:10:38.03,2,NTP,0,0,0,,还有有幸执导这部剧的导演\NAnd the directors' who've ever been very fortunate to come on the show
Dialogue: 0,2:10:38.12,2:10:39.36,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你们造就了这一切\NYou have done all of that
Dialogue: 0,2:10:39.44,2:10:44.00,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还争取到了在新墨西哥州的拍摄权\NAnd more,you've given credence filming here in New Mexico
Dialogue: 0,2:10:44.10,2:10:48.18,2,NTP,0,0,0,,和你所见过的首屈一指的工作人员一起合作\NWith a crew that is second to none,as you have met
Dialogue: 0,2:10:52.15,2:10:56.47,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心里满是你们的爱与支持 还有你们的才华\NMy heart is full with all your love and support and talent
Dialogue: 0,2:10:57.53,2:11:00.32,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们非常感谢你们 愿上帝保佑你们\NAnd we thank you so much and god bless you all
Dialogue: 0,2:11:13.44,2:11:15.50,2,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 天呐 看这是什么\NOh my goodness look at that
Dialogue: 0,2:11:23.02,2:11:24.76,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我会很想念你们的\NI'm gonna miss you guys so much
Dialogue: 0,2:11:25.48,2:11:27.75,2,NTP,0,0,0,,好难过啊\NIt's terrible,this is awful
Dialogue: 0,2:11:29.88,2:11:32.48,2,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 我不想承认\NIt really is,I mean,such denial
Dialogue: 0,2:11:34.27,2:11:38.67,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你们每天精神充沛地 热情洋溢地来做这份工作\NYou guys,every single day you come with such passion and excitement for this job
Dialogue: 0,2:11:38.75,2:11:43.82,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是 所以我们非常感谢你们\NAs do all we,so we all appreciate it,thank you
Dialogue: 0,2:11:43.91,2:11:48.69,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Vince 天呐 谢谢你\NVince Gilligan,my god,thank you
Dialogue: 0,2:11:48.79,2:11:54.83,2,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你创造了这样一部 出色的疯狂的危险的伟大的电视剧\NFor creating such a brilliant,crazy,dangerous and great show
Dialogue: 0,2:11:55.85,2:11:59.03,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么感谢你都不足为过\NI cannot thank you enough
Dialogue: 0,2:11:59.96,2:12:01.73,2,NTP,0,0,0,,Bryan\NBryan
Dialogue: 0,2:12:09.47,2:12:14.34,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是  我很爱你\NI just,I love you man,you know
Dialogue: 0,2:12:14.41,2:12:18.85,2,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊啊 喵了个咪 我爱你啊 你知道的\NAh god,damn it,I love you man,you know it
Dialogue: 0,2:12:18.93,2:12:22.07,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很幸运有你做我们剧的主角\NWe are so lucky to have this man be our no.1 on the show
Dialogue: 0,2:12:22.91,2:12:24.93,2,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们再鼓一次掌吧\NYou know,let's just have another round of applause
Dialogue: 0,2:12:29.46,2:12:32.94,2,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的让我成了一个更好的演员\NYou truly have made me become such a better actor
Dialogue: 0,2:12:33.03,2:12:36.63,2,NTP,0,0,0,,更好的人\NAnd I truly believe,a better person
Dialogue: 0,2:12:36.74,2:12:37.64,2,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\NSo thank you
Dialogue: 0,2:12:41.42,2:12:44.25,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得在我们拍第一季的时候\NI remember we were shooting in the first season
Dialogue: 0,2:12:44.33,2:12:46.58,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又在某个尘土飞扬的地方拍戏\NAnd we were rolling around another dirt somewhere and
Dialogue: 0,2:12:46.63,2:12:49.47,2,NTP,0,0,0,,在吃午饭的路上你说\NWe were walking to lunch and you said
Dialogue: 0,2:12:49.54,2:12:51.01,2,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这是不是太棒了\NAh,isn't this great
Dialogue: 0,2:12:51.09,2:12:52.78,2,NTP,0,0,0,,脸上都是汗水和尘土\NFull sweat and sand
Dialogue: 0,2:12:53.63,2:12:56.62,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得我跟你说 我说我希望你是这么觉得的\NAnd I remember telling you,I said man that's my hope for you
Dialogue: 0,2:12:56.71,2:13:00.77,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你会永远记住 我们是时间上最幸运的人\NThat you always remember that,that we are the luckiest people in the world
Dialogue: 0,2:13:00.86,2:13:03.05,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们真的明白\NWe truly know that,understand that
Dialogue: 0,2:13:04.55,2:13:12.37,2,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们会永远联系在一起 互助 友爱 我爱你 -我也爱你\NWe'll be forever tied,thankfully,lovingly,I love you -I love you too
Dialogue: 0,2:13:19.75,2:13:21.39,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不觉得这部剧是我独有的\NI don't really feel ownership
Dialogue: 0,2:13:22.43,2:13:27.45,2,NTP,0,0,0,,与其说是所有者 我觉得我更像是股东 如果这说得通的话\NI feel like a shareholder instead of an owner if that make sense
Dialogue: 0,2:13:28.22,2:13:30.82,2,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能达到如今的程度是经过了很多人的努力的\NIt went through so many hands to get here
Dialogue: 0,2:13:30.93,2:13:35.58,2,NTP,0,0,0,,幕前幕后的很多人都做出了贡献\NSo many people in front of the camera,behind the camera contributed
Dialogue: 0,2:13:35.67,2:13:37.91,2,NTP,0,0,0,,造就了这部剧\NAnd made this what it is
Dialogue: 0,2:13:39.09,2:13:40.86,2,NTP,0,0,0,,拍大合照啦 房车那边\NPhoto guys,down by the RV
Dialogue: 0,2:13:42.26,2:13:46.63,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这种大家庭凝聚的感觉很好\NIt's just been a wonderful feeling of family,of cohesion
Dialogue: 0,2:13:46.74,2:13:50.90,2,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人聚集在一起 我都不知道这一切是怎么发生的\NAll these people come together,I don't remember how it happened exactly
Dialogue: 0,2:13:53.60,2:13:54.92,2,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是命中注定一样\NIt just seemed to happened
